Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 
15. Ariyavagga 
153. Anussaritabbasutta 
“Anussaritabbañca vo, bhikkhave, dhammaṃ desessāmi na anussaritabbañca. 
Taṃ suṇātha … pe … 
katamo ca, bhikkhave, na anussaritabbo dhammo? 
Micchādiṭṭhi … pe … micchāvimutti—
ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, na anussaritabbo dhammo. 
Katamo ca, bhikkhave, anussaritabbo dhammo? 
Sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāvimutti—
ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, anussaritabbo dhammo”ti. 
Navamaṃ. 
